The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Paul S. Koehler, Appellant.

Judgment unanimously affirmed. Counsel’s application to withdraw granted (see, People v Crawford, 71 AD2d 38). (Appeal from judgment of Genesee County Court, Morton, J. — violation of probation.) Present— Dillon, P. J., Green, Pine, Balio and Davis, JJ.
